02:04:09,509 --> 02:04:11,568
Don't let me see your face
till next month...

1008
02:04:11,645 --> 02:04:15,877
'cause something tells me
I'm about to lose my famous kind streak.

1009
02:05:07,267 --> 02:05:10,634
My parents...

1010
02:05:10,704 --> 02:05:12,797
died...

1011
02:05:12,872 --> 02:05:17,502
in a car accident
four weeks ago.

1012
02:05:17,577 --> 02:05:19,545
It was terrible.

1013
02:05:22,015 --> 02:05:25,815
We didn't have the time to get to know
one another when you first came here...

1014
02:05:25,885 --> 02:05:30,652
but I want you to know I'm not the kind
of woman who'd let down a child...

1015
02:05:30,690 --> 02:05:33,989
whatever her situation,
whatever her mistake.

1016
02:05:34,060 --> 02:05:39,259
So I'm going to help you and do my best
to welcome you here again.

1017
02:05:41,034 --> 02:05:43,730
But on one condition:

1018
02:05:43,803 --> 02:05:46,966
You have to stop lying to me,
Mathilda.

1019
02:05:47,040 --> 02:05:49,338
I want you to take a chance...

1020
02:05:49,409 --> 02:05:52,344
and trust me.

1021
02:05:52,379 --> 02:05:54,847
Tell me what happened to you.

1022
02:05:58,351 --> 02:06:01,411
My family got shot down
by D.E.A. Officers...

1023
02:06:01,488 --> 02:06:04,855
because of a drug problem.

1024
02:06:04,924 --> 02:06:07,552
I left with the greatest guy on Earth.

1025
02:06:07,627 --> 02:06:12,428
He was a hit man, the best in town,
but he died this morning.

1026
02:06:12,499 --> 02:06:16,401
If you don't help me,
I'll be dead by tonight.

1027
02:06:35,722 --> 02:06:39,419
- You know her?
- I've never seen her.

1028
02:07:05,919 --> 02:07:08,615
I think we'll be okay here.